---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import '../styles/home.css';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Solo Mom by Choice — Intentional by Design"
  description="Clarity and support for professional women navigating solo motherhood."
>
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <p class="hero-label">Your Fertility Journey, Simplified</p>
      <h1 class="sr-only">Solo Mom Intentional — Clarity and Support for Your Fertility Journey</h1>
      <img src="/images/LisaLogo.png" alt="Solo Mom by Choice — Intentional by Design" class="hero-logo" />
      <p class="hero-subtitle">Clarity and support for professional women navigating solo motherhood.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <main class="container">
    <div class="cards-grid">
      <div class="card session-highlight">
        <h2>30-Minute Private Session</h2>
        <p>A 30-minute private session where I guide women through the donor conception and single-motherhood-by-choice decision-making process with real-life insight, emotional support, and clear next steps.</p>
        <p style="margin-top: 16px;">Designed specifically for professional women who are considering becoming Solo Moms by Choice or who have already begun the journey — but feel overwhelmed, unsure, or alone.</p>

        <p class="card-subheading">This Session Gives You</p>
        <ul class="benefits-list">
          <li>A safe, confidential space to ask anything about becoming a Solo Mom by Choice</li>
          <li>Clarity on egg freezing, IVF, PGT-A, and transfers</li>
          <li>Support navigating the emotional and logistical parts of the journey</li>
          <li>Guidance on balancing single motherhood and a demanding career</li>
        </ul>

        <div class="card-note">
          <strong>Bonus:</strong> The Solo Mom by Choice Cheat Sheet (PDF takeaway)
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2>Who This Session Is Perfect For</h2>
        <p>Professional women who are:</p>
        <ul class="benefits-list">
          <li>Considering becoming a Solo Mom by Choice</li>
          <li>Unsure where to start</li>
          <li>Feeling overwhelmed by donor selection</li>
          <li>Confused about IVF, meds, vials, and timelines</li>
          <li>Wanting actionable clarity, not vague advice</li>
          <li>Wishing they had support from someone who actually lived the journey</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="card agenda-card">
        <h2>Session Agenda</h2>

        <div class="agenda-item">
          <div class="agenda-time">2-3 min</div>
          <div class="agenda-content">
            <h3>Quick Welcome</h3>
            <p>Where are you in the process? What's top of mind?</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="agenda-item">
          <div class="agenda-time">20 min</div>
          <div class="agenda-content">
            <h3>Your Top Questions</h3>
            <p>We focus on what matters most to you:</p>
            <ul class="agenda-topics">
              <li>Donor selection</li>
              <li>Egg freezing</li>
              <li>IVF & PGT-A</li>
              <li>Transfer decisions</li>
              <li>Emotional readiness</li>
              <li>Career planning & timing</li>
              <li>Cost expectations</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="agenda-item">
          <div class="agenda-time">5 min</div>
          <div class="agenda-content">
            <h3>Clear Next Steps</h3>
            <p>You walk away with a personalized plan so you know exactly what to do next.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card-highlight">
          <p><strong>PDF Follow-Up:</strong> The Solo Mom by Choice Cheat Sheet</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="cta-section">
      <div class="cta-testimonial cta-testimonial-left">
        <p class="cta-testimonial-text">"Lisa's knowledge of the IVF process is incredibly thoughtful and practical. She helped me understand what to expect, ask the right questions, and feel more confident in my decisions."</p>
        <p class="cta-testimonial-author">— Addi, Account Executive</p>
      </div>
      <div class="cta-content">
        <h2>Ready to Get Started?</h2>
        <p>Book your 30-minute session and take the first step with clarity and confidence.</p>
        <a href="/book" class="cta-button">Book Your Session</a>
      </div>
      <div class="cta-testimonial cta-testimonial-right">
        <p class="cta-testimonial-text">"Lisa normalized everything I was feeling and helped me approach it with confidence instead of fear. And now I have healthy eggs for when I am ready."</p>
        <p class="cta-testimonial-author">— Lindsay, Account Director</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
